Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:46.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}彷彿一望無際
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:53.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲傷已煙消雲散
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.38,0:23:00.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}為了不讓這份笑容黯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:08.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}我會一直在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:12.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}沒有淚水的明天過後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:16.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}會有溫柔的未來等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:23.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即便是微弱的希望 也相信著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:27.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life一定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.04,0:23:30.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Feel you heart 只屬於自己的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:35.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}迷茫的時候攜手前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:37.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}在現實(現在)中Survive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:41.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life會和你一同發現
